description: Travel is the movement of people between distant geographical locations. Travel can be done by foot, bicycle, automobile, train, boat, bus, airplane, ship or other means, with or without luggage, and can be one way or round trip. We have arranged a tour with all of this. Sometimes we will walk, sometimes we will travel by bus. We will enjoy every bit of nature
